title: Marta (Nena Daconte song)
data: "Marta" is the third official single from Nena Daconte's debut album He Perdido Los Zapatos. It was written by Joaquin Fanlo Gonzalez and Mai Meneses.[1] It charted No.16 in Nielsen ratings in 2005. The band made two videos. The first is with a borrowed white Golf GTI convertible. When they obtained better funding from Universal, they refilmed the video with a red Ford Mustang.[2] This 2000s rock song-related article is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it.
